
& sixth_sense
 
 >> Help: Sixth Sense (Advantage)
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Notifies you of all locks (AIs, friends, and enemies).
 
 Result: You see an emit (message) when someone (or something) locks you. The
 message varies based on the unit's tonnage that is locking you.
 
 For a detailed look at this advantage, see our online documentation:
 docs.btmux.com/index.php/Skills%2C_Stats%2C_Attributes%2C_and_Advantages
 
